      "content": "i get that it might make me groggy but i really need to get some sleep tonight. it was just one glass, not like i'm drunk or anything. wouldn't a tiny bit of alcohol actually be fine to help the medicine work better? i feel like it's not that big of a deal if i just take it now.",
